Proposition NtNat150. Let n,m be natural numbers. Then

  n \cdot m = m \cdot n.

Proof. [prove off] qed.


Proposition NtNat155. Let n,m,k be natural numbers. Then

  n \cdot (m + k) = (n \cdot m) + (n \cdot k).

